MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM <br>
+3 WIS, +3 INT, +20 MANA, +20 PR<br>
WT: 0.5<br>
Class: CLR, SHM, NEC, WIZ, MAG, ENC<br>
Race: HUM, ERU, HIE, DEF, HEF, DWF, GNM, IKS<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
The rare is “Zorglim the Dead” and drops crystallized pieces uncommonly and sometimes rarely a Crystallized Shadow Tunic.<br>
<br>
<br>
Grab the key and proceed to the next level, to get there head straight out from port in to the door and follow the hallway to the mirror, put the key on your coursor and click U.<br>
<br>
The Mirror Out:<br>
The Mirror Out on this level is on the far left-hand corner, there is a bookshelf, click on it to move it aside but be careful because 2 Students guard behind it. Kill them or run around them and click on the mirror. <br>
<br>
<br>
Drops on this level:<br>
Various Crystallized Armor Pieces<br>
Various Fading and Velium Weapons<br>
Various Gnome Skin Armor.<br>
